ygData.msgSnippet: Only about 1 week ago that Singnet got problems with Cerfnet. Its not the downloading part its the uploading part. My pings using Singnet to Prexus is 150
ygData.messageBody:
Only about 1 week ago that Singnet got problems with Cerfnet. Its not the
downloading part its the uploading part. My pings using Singnet to Prexus is
150 average as receiving and 200-400 as uploading. Using Pacnet its like
500-700 receiving and 400-1000 uploading. Singnet connected at 50666. Pacnet
connected at 45333.

Maybe Singnet users should email them and request for a fix asap.

Once the Singnet problem is fixed. I will use Singnet back again because
Pacnet is really slow (even downloading webpages).

BTW: For wizs. Attempt to do the Ice Comet Quest as soon as you think you
can. The Staff of the Wheel (dmg 10 delay 100 +10 int +10 hp +10 mana weight
1.0 [only!]) is simply a prized weapon when used with glowing stein. (total
combo of 20 int and some additional mana) This beats the Staff of the
Observers anytime.

If any of you would like to ask how I did it, as the Ice Comet Quest info
circulating on the net may not be accurate at all, feel free to email me.

Mazy
Level 48 Wizard
Prexus
